{"tid":2050511,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國駐英使館︰給予持有BNO護照的香港中國公民居英權是違背自身立場與承諾","createTime":"2020-06-04T07:34:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T02:33:38.000Z","uid":60281,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"57e66e7d1c76de0be4f046e147bcfd820ccc16ee","tid":2050511,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T07:34:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530133-20200604.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530133-20200604.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraY6ooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=b090728b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530133-20200604.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=aa1fd421\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530133-20200604.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n中國駐英使館發言人強調，香港回歸中國後，《中英聯合聲明》當中與英國有關的權利與義務，已經履行完畢，任何國家無權藉《聯合聲明》干預香港事務。至於英國國民海外護照(BNO)問題，英方曾經與中方互換備忘錄，明確承諾不給予持有BNO護照的香港中國公民居英權，如果英方執意單方面改變做法，不但違背自身立場與承諾，亦違反國際法與國際關係基本準則。"},{"pid":"6b0165ea80ebf83a4e572729930e701dead2aa27","tid":2050511,"uid":271894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T07:35:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有冇"},{"pid":"376af17138dcd439ada87fe53317b4dac0e987a9","tid":2050511,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T07:39:56.000Z","msg":"[思想武裝]我們不妨功利一點看待｢六四｣<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2049910\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2049910</a>"},{"pi